original_title: MOKU S.III EP. I - The Icelander-Quota
overview: A new semester has begun, but one thing is missing: an icelandic pony. As the new student Matthildur wanders the halls of the school, it becomes evident that everything is not quite what it seems. What secret’s are lurking in the dark past of Filmhøjskolen Møn?
tagline: Shall we make love behind the airplane grill?
title: MOKU S.III EP. I - The Icelander-Quota
